Software requirements: node js and express installed on machine

Running the server:
Enter "node http_server.js" in terminal

Get functions:
Go to "localhost:3000/api", "localhost:3000/api/square?num=3" in a browser 

Post functions:
Send post request through Postman to "localhost:3000/name" with username=xyz as x-www-form-urlencoded key-value pair

